text: Grażyna Błąd (born 1 March 1969) is a Polish rowing coxswain. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Złotów Category:Sportspeople from Greater Poland Voivodeship Category:Coxswains (rowing)
